### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Ver catálogo de productos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/store/products

### Registro de cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "cliente@clinicaveterinaria.es",
  "password": "Test1234!",
  "full_name": "Jose Luis"
}

### Ver mascotas disponibles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/adoptions

### Adoptar mascota (reemplaza TOKEN y UUID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/adoptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "pet_id": "UUID_DE_LA_MASCOTA"
}

### Ver ofertas exclusivas adoptantes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/store/products/exclusive
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Realizar pedido
POST http://localhost:3000/api/store/order
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "product_id": "UUID_DEL_PRODUCTO",
  "quantity": 1
}